OL,3,CMan who stabbed his wife to death in
OL,4,Ccar park is jailed for life for murder
OL,6,FA man who stabbed his wife to death in
OL,7,Fa Cardiff car park has been jailed for
OL,8,Fa minimum of 23 years for her murder.
OL,10,FThisara Weragalage, 38, stabbed his
OL,11,Fwife, Niwunhellage Dona Nirodha
OL,12,FKalpani (known as Nirodha), multiple
OL,13,Ftimes in a residential car park in the
OL,14,FRiverside area of Cardiff.
OL,16,FThe defendant pleaded guilty to murder
OL,17,Fat Newport Crown Court on January 12.
OL,18,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to a
OL,19,Fcharge of having an article with a
OL,20,Fblade or point.
