OL,6,FA sentencing hearing at Cardiff Crown
OL,7,FCourt heard the couple had been
OL,8,Fseparated for months but on the
OL,9,Fmorning of 21 August, 2025, Weragalage
OL,10,Fwent to the car park knowing his wife
OL,11,Fparked her car there.
OL,13,FThe court heard he had bought knives
OL,14,Fthe day before and used one of them to
OL,15,Fkill Nirodha.
