OL,6,FWeragalage was sentenced to life
OL,7,Fimprisonment and ordered to serve a
OL,8,Fminimum of 23 years and nine months,
OL,9,Fof which he will serve a minimum of 23
OL,10,Fyears and 91 days due to time already
OL,11,Fspent in custody.
OL,13,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,14,Fin court, Ms Kalpani's father said:
OL,15,F"My only daughter was Nirodha Kalpani
OL,16,FNiwunhella. She was a happy,
OL,17,Fmischievous, playful girl who
OL,18,Fcaptivated everyone's hearts as a
OL,19,Fchild.
