OL,6,F"She loved her mother and father
OL,7,Fdearly and was a very good friend to
OL,8,Fher friends. She was a sweet girl who
OL,9,Falso loved animals.
OL,11,F"I am 64 years old and my wife is also
OL,12,F64 years old. The pain and anguish we
OL,13,Ffelt when we were informed that our
OL,14,Fdaughter had been murdered cannot be
OL,15,Fdescribed in words. After the brutal
OL,16,Fmurder of our only daughter, all our
OL,17,Fhopes were ruined. Her loss is an
OL,18,Funbearable mental burden for the
OL,19,Ffamily.
