OL,6,F"We faced a lot of problems because
OL,7,Fthis crime took place abroad. We were
OL,8,Ffurther affected by communication
OL,9,Fdifficulties and economic hardships.
OL,10,FWe were further hurt and mentally
OL,11,Fdistressed after it was confirmed that
OL,12,Fthis crime was committed by our
OL,13,Fdaughter's husband. We still cannot
OL,14,Funderstand how he could have committed
OL,15,Fthis heinous crime, as we loved him
OL,16,Falso as much as we loved our daughter."
