OL,6,FEmma Davies, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService, said: "Thisara Weragalage
OL,8,Fplanned his attack, visiting the area
OL,9,Fseveral times leading up to it and
OL,10,Fbuying the murder weapon.
OL,12,F"His premeditation was a significant
OL,13,Ffactor in this shocking murder.
OL,15,F"The strong evidence presented by the
OL,16,FCrown Prosecution Service demonstrated
OL,17,Fhis intention and resulted in a guilty
OL,18,Fplea.
