OL,6,F"The Crown Prosecution Service are
OL,7,Fworking together with the police to
OL,8,Fbuild strong cases against those who
OL,9,Fperpetrate violence against women and
OL,10,Fgirls, and our prosecutors are making
OL,11,Fsure more victims of these abhorrent
OL,12,Fand devastating crimes receive the
OL,13,Fjustice they deserve.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts remain with the family
OL,16,Fand friends of Nirodha who have
OL,17,Fsuffered a tragic loss."
